full_text: In the end, I'm not 100% happy how I did this year, I know I was irresponsible, annoying, and generally bad... And I'm sorry for that. I never meant to hurt anyone, and cause any damage for anyone, and I really feel guilty. For those who can, please forgive me...
full_text(utf-8): b"In the end, I'm not 100% happy how I did this year, I know I was irresponsible, annoying, and generally bad... And I'm sorry for that. I never meant to hurt anyone, and cause any damage for anyone, and I really feel guilty. For those who can, please forgive me..."

full_text: That was also kinda a hard year to be because my mental problems started to show more often and it forced me to do very irrational things. I really hope I'll figure this out next year as I'm planning to go to psychiatrist and try find any way I could get more emotionally stable.
full_text(utf-8): b"That was also kinda a hard year to be because my mental problems started to show more often and it forced me to do very irrational things. I really hope I'll figure this out next year as I'm planning to go to psychiatrist and try find any way I could get more emotionally stable."

full_text: That was also my most active year as a Brony, I went to several cons and meetups in Poland to soak the pony atmosphere of Polish fandom - I really love that! Unfortunately I couldn't attend any abroad con like GalaCon or Czequestria but that may be fixed next year maybe.

full_text:
That was also year of my first live performances: 
- 5th Twilightmeet, Warsaw, February
- Snowfall Ponymeet 2019, Katowice, March
- Kucykon 2019, Warsaw, July
- Nightmare Night 2019, Warsaw, October/November

Each one of them was unique and I wanna thank to my amazing audience!

full_text: I managed to release 3 EPs this year (Midwinter Dreamscapes, Equestrian Journey and Interdimensional Friendship) and a few singles. I managed to get 2 EPs on physical media (cassette and digipack CD). At the end of the year I started completing studio gear, and it'll continue.
